Adv.talkWithFacial("000101",nil,X8,[[However, if the temperature of the gas remains constant, pressure is inversely proportional to volume. This is called Boyle's law, which is paired with Charles's law as the combined gas law.]],"VC_MC02_21_03_00_Novel_00018_MAsami")
